Title: Peinture murale Eos by Galtane - Basis White
Description: Washable Eos II paint for interiors: Deep matt, extraordinary coverage and perfect adhesion with a wealth of authentic and luminous mineral colours. Once applied, the painted surface is washable (class 2 according to the EN 13300 standard). The paint is guaranteed to be vegetable oil based.Please note that the entire composition is integral. Guaranteeing excellent adhesion, it can be applied to various new or old surfaces. Carefully read the technical data sheet and the table “Which primer? “and choose a quality roller.More info:– FR : https://www.galtane.com/fr/accueil/57-267-peinture-eos-ii.html#/30-contenance-1_l/50-couleurs-blanc_wit– NL : https://www.galtane.com/nl/home/57-267-peinture-eos-ii.html
